statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_metrics;
SELECT operation_name, performance_metric FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE error_rate < 0.01;
SELECT id, timestamp, error_rate FROM quantum_hardware_metrics ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE performance_metric > 0.8 ORDER BY performance_metric DESC;
SELECT operation_name, AVG(error_rate) AS avg_error_rate FROM quantum_hardware_metrics GROUP BY operation_name;
SELECT operation_name, error_rate FROM quantum_hardware_metrics ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE performance_metric > 0.9 ORDER BY performance_metric ASC;
SELECT id, operation_name, timestamp FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE error_rate < 0.05 ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE error_rate > 0.05 AND performance_metric < 0.8 ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 8;
SELECT AVG(error_rate), MAX(performance_metric) FROM quantum_hardware_metrics WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' GROUP BY operation_name ORDER BY operation_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_rates;
SELECT id, error_rate, timestamp FROM quantum_error_rates ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT operation_id, error_rate FROM quantum_error_rates WHERE error_rate > 0.05;
SELECT id, execution_time FROM quantum_performance_metrics WHERE success = true;
SELECT * FROM quantum_performance_metrics ORDER BY execution_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_error_rates WHERE error_rate > 0.01 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT operation_id, AVG(error_rate) FROM quantum_error_rates GROUP BY operation_id HAVING AVG(error_rate) > 0.05;
SELECT id, operation_id, timestamp FROM quantum_performance_metrics WHERE execution_time > 5 AND success = true ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT operation_id, COUNT(*) AS total_errors FROM quantum_error_rates GROUP BY operation_id ORDER BY total_errors DESC;
SELECT qem.id, qpm.execution_time FROM quantum_error_rates AS qer INNER JOIN quantum_performance_metrics AS qpm ON qer.operation_id = qpm.operation_id WHERE qer.error_rate < 0.005;
SELECT * FROM error_rates ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, error_rate FROM error_rates WHERE error_rate > 0.5;
SELECT operation_name FROM quantum_operations WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT id, execution_time FROM performance_metrics ORDER BY execution_time ASC;
SELECT id, timestamp FROM error_rates WHERE id = 3;
SELECT id, timestamp, error_rate FROM error_rates WHERE error_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM performance_metrics WHERE execution_time < 100 AND timestamp BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-06-30';
SELECT id, operation_name FROM quantum_operations WHERE operation_name LIKE '%gate%' ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT id, timestamp, execution_time FROM performance_metrics WHERE execution_time > 50 ORDER BY execution_time DESC, timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, timestamp, operation_name FROM quantum_operations WHERE timestamp > '2023-01-01' AND operation_name IN ('Hadamard', 'CNOT') ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM error_rates ORDER BY id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT operation_id, error_rate FROM error_rates WHERE error_rate > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM quantum_operations WHERE operation_type = 'Qubit' AND error_status = TRUE;
SELECT hardware_name, location FROM quantum_hardware ORDER BY hardware_name ASC;
SELECT operation_id, execution_time FROM performance_metrics WHERE execution_time < 10;
SELECT id, operation_id, error_rate FROM error_rates ORDER BY error_rate DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT operation_id, execution_time FROM performance_metrics WHERE execution_time > 5.0
SELECT * FROM quantum_operations WHERE error_status = true
SELECT operation_name, operation_type FROM quantum_operations WHERE operation_type = 'gate' ORDER BY operation_name
SELECT * FROM quantum_hardware WHERE hardware_type = 'superconducting'
SELECT * FROM error_rates;
SELECT error_type, error_code FROM error_rates WHERE error_type='Critical';
SELECT component_name, manufacturer, release_date FROM hardware_components ORDER BY release_date DESC;
SELECT operation_name, execution_time_ms FROM performance_metrics WHERE success=true;
SELECT operation_name, operation_type, quantum_gate FROM quantum_operations WHERE operation_type='Measurement';
SELECT * FROM error_rates WHERE error_code > 100 ORDER BY error_type DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT operation_name, execution_time_ms FROM performance_metrics WHERE success = true ORDER BY execution_time_ms ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT manufacturer FROM hardware_components WHERE release_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY manufacturer ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT operation_id, timestamp, log_message FROM operation_logs WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT operation_name, operation_type, quantum_gate FROM quantum_operations WHERE operation_type = 'Quantum Computing' ORDER BY operation_name ASC LIMIT 5;
